{"tid":512903,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我用iphone，關其他人咩事?","createTime":"2017-12-29T03:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T20:43:39.000Z","uid":32051,"like":139,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6832cd063176b060f14561f8fbebdf645c4448","tid":512903,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"點解用iphone就要俾an機機主屌？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我用iphone用得好開心，我唔覺得用佢好潮，或者咁講，那怕我覺得用佢潮都係我個人想法，只要我無因為用iphone而睇唔起其他人用an機，單純覺得佢簡單岩我心水，我就用佢，咁都唔得咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解用an機班人，日鬧夜鬧，你有你用an機，我有我用iphone。<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪我用iphone，比較敏感。<br />\n法國好多an機機主屌人用iphone，但我又唔多覺有iphone屌人用an機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實俾你屌完，我都係會繼續用iphone，你由得我依種垃圾用垃圾iphone啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dfdab3225f6112e178b3acbfd314684a9fdac3","tid":512903,"uid":52194,"like":56,"dislike":4,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"An自卑"},{"pid":"4cda16384c6222208f132a30f7056bf3f1864742","tid":512903,"uid":5843,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">因為想你買an機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"89daf3e66cb0c205bf4a0468ab6fc988255243bf","tid":512903,"uid":27609,"like":47,"dislike":12,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"幾歲？ 仲打埋d無謂野<br />\n以為返左2010"},{"pid":"5255279ae6b96f96f5ce29664f46225e2ac21ac7","tid":512903,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"89daf3e66cb0c205bf4a0468ab6fc988255243bf","tid":512903,"uid":27609,"like":47,"dislike":12,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"幾歲？ 仲打埋d無謂野<br />\n以為返左2010"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=